      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "p4rZI",
          "name": "utitle",
          "fill": "$text",
          "content": "📐  Usage Notes",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "FJ0zB",
          "name": "s1h",
          "fill": "$primary",
          "content": "Token Variable Reference",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 16,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "z6BK1",
          "name": "s1b",
          "fill": "$textSecondary",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 700,
          "content": "All components use design tokens via $variable syntax:\n• Colors:  $primary  $secondary  $accent  $background  $surface  $text  $border  $success  $error  $warning  $info\n• Spacing:  $xs(4)  $sm(8)  $md(12)  $lg(16)  $xl(24)  $xxl(32)\n• Radius:  $none(0)  $sm(6)  $md(10)  $lg(16)  $xl(20)  $pill(999) — use by role, not one size everywhere\n• Font sizes:  $h1(28)  $h2(22)  $h3(18)  $body(14)  $bodySmall(12)  $caption(10)",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 12,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "X4RAo",
          "name": "s2h",
          "fill": "$primary",
          "content": "Typography ",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 16,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "NIOlI",
          "name": "s2b",
          "fill": "$textSecondary",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 700,
          "content": "Font: Inter (Google Fonts, free commercial use)\n• $fontFamily = \"Inter\" — proportional, for all UI text\n• Recommended sizes: 10, 12, 13, 14, 16, 18, 20, 22, 28px\n• Button text: Inter Bold 18px, always centered\n• Body text: Inter Regular 13-14px at 67% opacity white",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 12,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "tx1zY",
          "name": "s3h",
          "fill": "$primary",
          "content": "Component Naming Convention",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 16,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "Qvc0A",
          "name": "s3b",
          "fill": "$textSecondary",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 700,
          "content": "All components follow: Component / Variant / State\n• Example: Button/primary/default, Button/secondary/hover, Card/outlined, Tabs/pills\n• Common variants: primary, secondary, success, danger, elevated, outlined, filled, soft\n• Common states: default, hover, pressed, disabled, focused, error, open",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 12,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "asZuH",
          "name": "s4h",
          "fill": "$primary",
          "content": "Button Gradient Formula",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 16,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "yvhZb",
          "name": "s4b",
          "fill": "$textSecondary",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 700,
          "content": "Every button follows: gradient fill + pill radius (999px) + matching outer glow shadow\n• Gold:  #FFD54F → #F0A030, glow: #F0A03060\n• Green: #2ECC71 → #1DA855, glow: #1DA85560\n• Blue:  #4A8BF5 → #3366CC, glow: #3366CC60\n• Cancel: solid #3D2A8A + 1.5px border",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 12,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "FFZVJ",
          "name": "s5h",
          "fill": "$primary",
          "content": "UrhoX Integration",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 16,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "hpRa1",
          "name": "s5b",
          "fill": "$textSecondary",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 700,
          "content": "Target: UrhoX UI (Yoga layout + NanoVG rendering + Lua 5.4)\n• Export tokens → Lua table or JSON for runtime theming\n• borderRadius maps to nvgRoundedRect() using the token radius scale\n• Gradients map to nvgLinearGradient() for buttons and backgrounds\n• Glow shadows map to nvgBoxGradient() with blur parameter",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 12,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
